理能力</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >协调能力</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >沟通能力</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >组织能力</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >创新能力</th></tr></thead><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >协调能力</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >2</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >5</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >4</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >沟通能力</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1/2</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >4</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >2</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >组织能力</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1/5</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1/4</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >2</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >创新能力</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1/4</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1/2</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1/2</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1</td></tr></tbody></table></table-wrap><p>表4. 二级指标相对于一级指标管理能力的判断矩阵</p><table-wrap id="table5" ><label><xref ref-type="table" rid="table5">Table 5</xref></label><caption><title> Judgment matrix for practice ability of the secondary index compared with the first inde</title></caption><table><tbody><thead><tr><th align="center" valign="middle" >实践能力</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >科学实践能力</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >社会实践能力</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >生产实践能力</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >教育实践能力</th></tr></thead><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >科学实践能力</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >2</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >4</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >3</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >社会实践能力</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1/2</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >