><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/4-2580203x41_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><disp-formula id="hanspub.19250-formula185"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/4-2580203x42_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><disp-formula id="hanspub.19250-formula186"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/4-2580203x43_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><disp-formula id="hanspub.19250-formula187"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/4-2580203x44_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><disp-formula id="hanspub.19250-formula188"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/4-2580203x45_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>在对评价对象进行模糊综合评价时，研究小组在GJ集团选取甲员工作为评价对象，对甲进行人岗匹配的测评 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.19250-ref6">6</xref>] 。根据岗位评价指标综合素质、管理能力、实践能力以及学习能力，将其划分为五个评价等</p><table-wrap id="table6" ><label><xref ref-type="table" rid="table6">Table 6</xref></label><caption><title> Judgment matrix for learning ability of the secondary index compared with the first inde</title></caption><table><tbody><thead><tr><th align="center" valign="middle" >学习能力</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >解决问题能力</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >逻辑思维能力</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >自学能力</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >阅读能力</th></tr></thead><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >解决问题能力</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >3</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >4</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >4</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >逻辑思维能力</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1/3</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >2</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >3</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >自学能力</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1/4</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1/2</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >3</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >阅读能力</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1/4</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1/3</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1/3</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1</td></tr></tbody></table></table-wrap><p>表6. 二级指标相对于一级指标学习能力的判断矩阵</p><p>级，给出甲员工的指标评价分值，研究小组对评价的结果进行分析整理后得到甲的人岗匹配评价矩阵，如表7所示。</p><p>评价甲对象综合素质、管理能力、实践能力、学习能力指标所属各因素的模糊判断矩阵分别为：</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19250-formula189"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/4-2580203x46_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><disp-formula id="hanspub.19250-formula190"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/4-2580203x47_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>分别计算出甲综合素质、管理能力、实践能力、学习能力指标的模糊综合评价矩阵为：</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19250-formula191"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/4-2580203x48_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><disp-formula id="hanspub.19250-formula192"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/4-2580203x49_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><disp-formula id="hanspub.19250-formula193"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/4-2580203x50_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><disp-formula id="hanspub.19250-formula194"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/4-2580203x51_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>评价对象甲的一级指标所属各因素评价分值构成的模糊判断矩阵为：</p><table-wrap id="table7" ><label><xref ref-type="table" rid="table7">Table 7</xref></label><caption><title> Person-post matching table of a cler</title></caption><table><tbody><thead><tr><th align="center" valign="middle"  colspan="2"   rowspan="2"  >评价指标</th><th align="center" valign="middle"  colspan="5"  >评价等级集</th></tr></thead><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >很匹配</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >匹配</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >比较匹配</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >一般匹配</td><td align="cente